        "subject": "LU-2466 lnet: LNET Hash Table Testing for 2.4.0",
        "message": "LU-2466 lnet: LNET Hash Table Testing for 2.4.0\n\nThe test plan for the Remote Networks Hash Table\ncalls for full regression testing and unit tests for\nthe default hash table size of 64 and a size of 1070.\n\nHash table size can be found in dmesg by looking for\n\"hash table\".\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly testgroup=full\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia30802ff56949e9de3bb682225ec43409c0be5fb\n"
      },
